wiki.content: instagram 2017.12.26 DEAN Lyrics/작사: Deanfluenza Composer/작곡: Deanfluenza, highhopes Arranger/편곡: Deanfluenza, highhopes How did you come to create the song "Instagram"? DEAN: I wanted to create an album that was fitting to me. I figured there wasn't much of a difference between people living in their 20s and 30s. So I thought many would agree with my honest views. I decided to observe myself and I realized that I used Instagram a lot, for no particular reason; just out of habit. I thought about writing a track on Instagram. And I also found out that I became very depressed after using Instagram. I tend to follow many renown artists and realized how small I am compared to them. There are so many talented, pretty and handsome people out there. Soon, I started comparing myself to others and it was really difficult for me. That's when I decided to write a song about it. I thought others out there might be experiencing the same thing. I wanted to write a song about Robin Crusoe in a vast city. Read more on Last.fm.
